# Local

bundle install
rake db:migrate 

# Demo

## Create

heroku create ryancontact
git push heroku master

## Extend and Introspect

heroku addons:add memcache:5mb pgbackups:basic
heroku pgbackups:capture

heroku addons:upgrade logging:advanced
heroku logs --tail

## Scale

heroku dynos +2
heroku ps
heroku dynos 1

